      • Ingredient

        public Ingredient​(java.lang.String name,
                  java.lang.String description,
                  java.util.Date bestBeforeDate,
                  Constants.Location location,
                  java.lang.Integer amount,
                  Constants.AmountUnit unit,
                  Constants.IngredientCategory category)
        This is the loaded constructor for an Ingredient object. It contains all of the necessary parameters for instantiation.
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the ingredient (String).
        description - An optional description of the ingredient (String).
        bestBeforeDate - The expiry date in YYYY-MM-DD ISO Format (Date).
        location - The location where the ingredient is stored (Constants.Location).
        amount - The positive integer amount of the ingredient (Integer.
        unit - The unit the ingredient is stored by (Constants.AmountUnit).
        category - The food category that the ingredient falls under (Constants.IngredientCategory).
